<div>
<div  style="float: right; margin-right: 300px">
<h1> Discussion for: {{model.name}} </h1>
<h3>Discussion points:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Was it useful for you?</li>
  <li>At what point in the curriculum did you find it most helpful?</li>
  <li>Was it easy to digest</li>
  <li>What type of learner would benefit from this material?</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div  style="float: left; margin-left: 100px">
  <h1>New Review</h1>
  <div>
    <form>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="answer">Answer</label>
        {{input value=answer id="answer"}}
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="replier">Your name</label>
        {{input value=replier id="replier"}}
      </div>

      <button {{action 'saveAnswer'}}>Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
